survey_response.review_text: I had a seamless experience with Dr. Sowjanya and Dr. Soumya. My goal was to have an extra tooth removed and improve the appearance of my other teeth. I’m so glad I got my dental treatment under the expert & careful guidance of Dr.Sowjanya. Before consulting her, my teeth & gums were in a horrible state due to years of negligence & a botched bridge work.

The end results could not be better considering the options I was given by other doctors in the area.
I’d highly recommend Dr.Sowjanya for your dental treatments, no matter how big or small they are & be rest assured you’ll get the best advise & treatment there is.
